# Example Decision Logic

## If image contains:

```dockerfile
ubi9-minimal
```

Then DiP should generate:

```dockerfile
RUN yum --config=/etc/dnf/dnf.conf \
    --setopt=cachedir=/var/cache/microdnf \
    --setopt=reposdir=/etc/yum.repos.d \
    --setopt=varsdir=/etc/dnf \
    --installroot=/staging \
    --releasever=9 \
    --noplugins \
    install -y openssl
```

NOT generic `dnf install`.

